	<br><br>
	<p>The contemporary Aspen 2, one bedroom, one bath apartment home, located on the Edgemont&#39;s northwest side, offers its residents an excellent blend of upscale comfort, modern apartment home features and functionality. Measuring at a cozy 768 sq ft, this splendid one bedroom floor plan is designed with an open living and dining area, yet provides for an intimate setting and atmosphere, is complemented with beautiful laminate surface floors and a wood burning fireplace. Additionally, the Aspen 2 provides you with a complete array of wonderfully upscale apartment home amenity features, such as, ceiling mounted track lighting, granite counter tops, open air kitchen area with stainless steel kitchen appliances (including microwave oven), oak wood finish kitchen cabinetry, individual space saver washer dryer unit, dishwasher and large bedroom suite walk-in closet. Further enhancing your pleasurable living here at the Edgemont, is your spacious private balcony, on which you can enjoy a well deserved measure of peace and tranquility in the heart of Bethesda. We think the Aspen 2 is a &quot;great place for living space&quot;. Schedule a tour and see what we mean!
	<br>
	<p>The Edgemont at Bethesda Metro is within minutes walking distance of Bethesda Row and the downtown vicinity, with shopping, entertainment and a wide variety of restaurants to choose from for your dining out pleasure. We are also conveniently located  just two blocks west of the Bethesda Red Line Metro station.  Additionally, the Edgemont offers its residents reserved underground parking space, outdoor pool and patio with propane grills, and finally, look no further than our newly designed and constructed state-of-the-art fitness center for fine tuning your daily physical workout routine.
The Edgemont is in the perfect location!
